thread.title: Margaret

author: Margaret
title: Margaret
text: I called and spoke to the folks at Willis before I ordered. They talked to me about what I wanted, recommended 3 trees and I placed the order. The tress arrived shortly and the next day went into the ground. They have been planted for almost 2 weeks and so far they look healthy. I am very happy with the help and high quality of the trees. I see cherry pie in my future.
